metadata.name: Medici's Glittery Glasses
metadata.description:
This one is for Cozomo de'Medici, the Patron of the Digital Arts. This CrypT0 ArT commemorates #TheMediciCollection NFT NYC's most historic art event!

It also contains a question. Do you know anything about Cozomo de'Medici?
